track.name: Arms Around You (feat. Maluma & Swae Lee)

wiki.summary: On “Arms Around You,” XXXTENTACION, Swae Lee, and Maluma each sing about embracing a woman that they love. Lil Pump’s verse, however, is inconsistent with this theme as he raps about his wealth, drug use, and polygamous nature. This song can be considered a spiritual successor to “I don’t even speak spanish lol,” a mostly Spanish song from X’s sophomore studio album ?. Read more on Last.fm.
